Released 27th April.

Hassle release this limited split from two of their finest artists. Rolo offer up an exclusive track while Cancer Bats' side is cover of dance-punks The Faint(!?). Never thought I'd type that.

A. Cancer Bats - Agenda Suicide

B. Rolo Tomassi - Jealous Bones
